      mid: '~$300–700 (the sweet spot): Seiko 5 SRPG-series and SRPE field models (~$250–300, 4R36 auto), Hamilton Khaki Field Mechanical 38mm (~$475–550, hand-wound H-50, 80h reserve), Hamilton Khaki Field Auto (~$650–750, H-10 auto), and Marathon General Purpose Mechanical/Navigator. This band is where most enthusiasts land.',
