      mid: 'approx. USD 1,000-6,000: mechanical chronographs with real heritage. Hamilton Intra-Matic Chronograph (~$2,000+), Tissot PRS-516 / PR 516 chronograph, and TAG Heuer Carrera chronographs (~$2,300 for simpler Calibre 5 models, ~$4,000-6,000 for Calibre 16 / TH20 in-house chronographs).',
