      mid: '~$1,000–6,000: Swiss skeletons and open-hearts with real finishing. Tissot T-Complication Squelette and Chemin des Tourelles (~€1,200+), Hamilton Jazzmaster Skeleton (~$1,500, 80h ETA C07), Frederique Constant Heart Beat / Slimline (~€2,000), Rado Anatom/True Skeleton, Oris.',
